body:
Hi @satok16 , I tried in 3.0/3.1 as well, 
Release build is working fine.
when i tried `android_Debug_aarch64`,
`debug` option gets set somehow and **it has side effects of inception version getting set to 1**

under version 1: toinception_dummy_int_data_224x224 gets used.

i have added new changes in glue to build for android_Debug_aarch64 and pick proper adspmsgd in target/make/android.min.

so could you help in checking below part:
`debug` option gets set somehow and **it has side effects of inception version getting set to 1**

thanks,
